# end()

**Instance Method**

Ends a suspension.

## Declaration

```swift
func end()
```

## Discussion

If this is the last suspension, the coordinator adjusts the timing of its playback object to match the group.

To end a suspension and simultaneously propose a new playback time to the group, call the [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVCoordinatedPlaybackSuspension/end(proposingNewTime:)] method.

## Ending a suspension

- **end(proposingNewTime:)**: Ends a suspension and proposes a new playback time to the group.
